OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome evening sunshine, turning
OL,7,Fcloudier at times during the night,
OL,8,Fperhaps some patchy rain reaching
OL,9,FOrkney by dawn. Quite a cool night.
OL,10,FNortherly winds turning southeasterly.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA bright start for Shetland
OL,13,Fbut cloudier with some light rain at
OL,14,Ffirst for Orkney. turning into a wet
OL,15,Fafternoon with showery rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
